Tested byTestaro, procedure ts24
Scored byTestilo, procedure tsp24
Digested byTestilo, procedure tdp24

Introduction

This is a digest of results from a battery of accessibility Tests.

The battery includes 1353 automated accessibility tests drawn from ten different packages: Alfa, Axe, Continuum, Equal Access, HTML CodeSniffer, Nu Html Checker, QualWeb, Tenon, Testaro, and WAVE.

These tests were run on the web page named above and gave the page a score of 1162, where 0 would be perfect.

Issue summary

Special issues

log: Score 70. This is based on the amount of browser error logging and miscellaneous logging during the tests.

solos: Score 22. This is based on issues reported by unclassified tests. Details are in the report.

Classified issues

Issue linkIndication

WCAG: 1.3.3

Score: 117

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package testaro, test linkUl, score 114 (Non-underlined adjacent links)
  • Package alfa, test r62, score 2 (Inline link is not distinct from the surrounding text except by color)

Issue contentBeyondLandmarks

WCAG: 1.3.6

Score: 94

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package alfa, test r57, score 50 (Perceivable text content is not included in any landmark)
  • Package axe, test region, score 11 (Some page content is not contained by landmarks)
  • Package ibm, test Rpt_Aria_OrphanedContent_Native_Host_Sematics, score 68 (Content does not reside within an element with a landmark role)

Issue linkNoText

WCAG: 2.4.4

Score: 87

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package alfa, test r11, score 24 (Link has no accessible name)
  • Package axe, test link-name, score 18 (Link has no discernible text)
  • Package continuum, test 237, score 24 (a element has no mechanism that allows an accessible name value to be calculated)
  • Package htmlcs, test e:AAA.4_1_2.H91.A.EmptyNoId, score 4 (Link has no name or id attribute or value)
  • Package htmlcs, test e:AAA.4_1_2.H91.A.NoContent, score 20 (Link has an href attribute but no text)
  • Package ibm, test WCAG20_A_HasText, score 24 (Hyperlink has no text description)
  • Package wave, test e:link_empty, score 28 (Link contains no text)
  • Package tenon, test 57, score 28 (Link has no text inside it)

Score: 74

  • Package qualWeb, test QW-ACT-R62, score 69 (Element in the sequential focus order has no visible focus)
